# Navigation Rule

- Use the left sidebar and top navigation as defined in [components/navigation/left-navigation.tsx](mdc:components/navigation/left-navigation.tsx) and [components/navigation/top-header.tsx](mdc:components/navigation/top-header.tsx).
- Tab navigation within pages should use the `tabs` prop of PageShell and [ContentTabs](mdc:components/navigation/content-tabs.tsx).
- Only include required submenu items (e.g., VPC, Subnets, Security Groups, Static IPs) as per product requirements.
- Do not add or remove navigation items without product/design approval.
